                <faqs
                    jcr:created="{Date}2022-09-12T11:32:18.320-03:00"
                    jcr:createdBy="admin"
                    jcr:lastModified="{Date}2022-10-19T09:38:27.808-05:00"
                    jcr:lastModifiedBy="admin"
                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                    sling:resourceType="airmiles-ai/components/faqs"
                    moreInfoText="&lt;p>If you any other question or request please reach us at: &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:%20user@airmiles.ai&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>info@airmiles.ai&lt;/a>&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
                    textIsRich="[true,true,true,true,true,true,true,true,true,true,true]">
                    <questionsAnswers jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured">
                        <item0
                            jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                            answer="&lt;p>Through our platform there are three solutions; the Reporting &amp;amp; Analytics platform, the Data Sharing platform, and A-MAP. Each tool provides access to business &amp;amp; customer data and metrics. &lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>The &lt;b>Reporting &amp;amp; Analytics&lt;/b> platform provides fast, automated access to reports &amp;amp; dashboard so you can easily understand your business and customer performance.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>The &lt;b>Data Sharing&lt;/b> platform allows access to aggregated and customer-level data to develop your own analyses, and uncover insights and reports to help improve your marketing metrics.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>&lt;b>A-Map&lt;/b> is a geo-spatial analytics tool that visually represents customer metrics and behaviors on a map, by location.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>With each of these tools you can quickly access information to better understand your business and customers, helping you make better data-driven decisions.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
                            question="&lt;p>What data &amp;amp; analytics solutions are offered by AIR MILES&lt;sup>®&lt;/sup> Reward Program?&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"/>
                        <item1
                            jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                            answer="&lt;p>We provide access to tabular, graphical and geographical reporting and data sharing across AIR MILES&lt;sup>®&lt;/sup> Reward Program’s vast first party data sets to support partner-driven tactical and strategic decision making. Our solution can help you get to know your customers’ demographics, trade area and retail playbook. You can optimize your campaign through machine learning and self-service personalization and automation. Marketing personalization is key to serving millions of customers customized offer recommendations with basket penetrations while getting to know these customers deeper with personalized KPI's.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
                            question="What kind of reports and dashboards are available?"/>
                        <item2
                            jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                            answer="&lt;p>With our solutions, you’ll be able to get fast access to performance results &amp;amp; customer insights. With this information, you’ll be able to improve marketing effectiveness, identify your best customers, and optimize marketing campaigns.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
                            question="&lt;p>How can I make use of AIR MILES&lt;sup>®&lt;/sup> dashboards &amp;amp; reports?&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"/>
                        <item3
                            jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                            answer="&lt;p>You’ll enjoy:&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;ul>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>Access to multiple marketing metrics through our automated reports, which can be accessed via web or mobile&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>24/7 availability &amp;amp; access to reports&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>Automated updating of reports&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>Easily customized reports via filtering&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;/ul>&#xd;&#xa;"
                            question="&lt;p>What additional benefits can I get as an AIR MILES&lt;sup>®&lt;/sup> partner?&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"/>
                        <item4
                            jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                            answer="&lt;p>You can contact us using our form and we will get in touch as soon as possible.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
                            question="How can I sign up or learn more about the analytics &amp;amp; intelligence solution?"/>
                    </questionsAnswers>
                </faqs>
